the evening when she's here.

1105
01:20:04,700 --> 01:20:06,800
Oh, let me see that ring.

1106
01:20:09,400 --> 01:20:12,000
[ Gasps ]
Oh, wow. Look at that.

1107
01:20:15,600 --> 01:20:18,600
