to invite her down, Maggie.

1135
01:21:39,700 --> 01:21:41,200
I don't know
where you got that idea.

1136
01:21:41,700 --> 01:21:44,200
Maggie,
I specifically asked you to.

1137
01:21:44,900 --> 01:21:48,000
