1152
01:22:47,200 --> 01:22:48,800
She was special.

1153
01:22:49,200 --> 01:22:51,200
Different than the other moms.

1154
01:22:51,800 --> 01:22:53,400
She used to surprise us.

1155
01:22:56,600 --> 01:22:58,900
One time I opened up
my lunch box...

1156
